import cadquery as cq

h = 20
ir = 10
or_ = 40
cog_width = 20
cog_height = 10
cog_thickness = h
num_cogs = 6
cog_insert = 2

gear = cq.Workplane("XY").gear(teeth=num_cogs, module=(or_-ir)/num_cogs, pressure_angle=20, height=h, clearance=0).extrude(h)
cog = cq.Workplane("XY").rect(cog_width, cog_height).extrude(cog_thickness).translate((0, or_+cog_insert+cog_height/2, h/2))

for i in range(num_cogs):
    angle = i * 360 / num_cogs
    r = gear.union(cog.rotate((0, 0, 0), (0, 0, 1), angle))
